pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 40, 1000, 40]
    content:
      style: "$pageTitle"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Solution : Cartographie Interactive Collaborative</strong></p>
  - elementId: title-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 85, 100, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 3, color: "$accent"}
  - elementId: feat1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 115, 370, 220]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$white"
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$light"}
  - elementId: feat1-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [80, 130, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fas:sitemap"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: feat1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 178, 330, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Flowchart Interactif</strong></p>
  - elementId: feat1-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 210, 330, 110]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>14 etapes du processus commercial visualisees. Cliquez pour voir la description, les actions et les documents attendus.</p>
  - elementId: feat2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [455, 115, 370, 220]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$white"
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$light"}
  - elementId: feat2-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [475, 130, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fas:folder-tree"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: feat2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [475, 178, 330, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Organisation Hierarchique</strong></p>
  - elementId: feat2-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [475, 210, 330, 110]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>Entreprise &gt; Projet AIM-XXXX &gt; Dossier par etape &gt; Fichier. Structure identique a votre processus existant.</p>
  - elementId: feat3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [850, 115, 370, 220]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$white"
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$light"}
  - elementId: feat3-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [870, 130, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fas:user-shield"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: feat3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [870, 178, 330, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Roles &amp; Permissions (RBAC)</strong></p>
  - elementId: feat3-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [870, 210, 330, 110]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>3 roles : Commercial, Directeur, Admin. Chaque role a des permissions specifiques sur les projets et documents.</p>
  - elementId: feat4-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 360, 560, 130]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: feat4-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [80, 380, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:cloud"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$white"
  - elementId: feat4-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [125, 375, 480, 100]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p><strong>Synchronisation Cloud</strong></p>
        <p><span style="font-size:14px; color:#FFFFFFCC;">Donnees persistantes via Firebase Firestore. Acces multi-appareils en temps reel. LocalStorage comme fallback offline.</span></p>
  - elementId: feat5-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [660, 360, 560, 130]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: feat5-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [680, 380, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:share-nodes"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$white"
  - elementId: feat5-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [725, 375, 480, 100]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p><strong>Partage avec Autorisation</strong></p>
        <p><span style="font-size:14px; color:#FFFFFFCC;">Le proprietaire partage son projet en mode viewer ou editor. Le directeur doit demander l'autorisation pour modifier.</span></p>
  - elementId: flow-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 520, 1160, 110]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.8
      align: [center, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong style="color:#1E3A5F;">PROCESSUS :</strong> Reception d'offre  &gt;  Pre-etude  &gt;  Definition SCOP  &gt;  Metro TakeOff  &gt;  Etude exigences</p>
        <p>&gt;  Montage/Fabrication + Fournisseur/Sous-traitants  &gt;  Chiffrage  &gt;  Preparation offre</p>
        <p>&gt;  Suivi/Negociation  &gt;  Verification contrat  &gt;  Harmonisation  &gt;  Passation  &gt;  Gestion  &gt;  Bilan</p>
  - elementId: bottom-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 660, 1160, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$light"}
  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1150, 670, 70, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "05"
